B16 <> C6 B10 [weight:0]
B15 <> A3 B12 [weight:3]
B15 <> A6 B9 [weight:0]
B15 <> C6 B9 [weight:0]
B14 <> A4 B10 [weight:0]
B14 <> C6 B8 [weight:0]
B12 <> F'12 [weight:1]
B12 <> A3 B9 [weight:1]
A3 B12 <> A3 A4 B8 [weight:0]
A6 B12 <> A6 A4 B8 [weight:0]
C6 B12 <> C6 A4 B8 [weight:0]
) B12 <> ) A4 B8 [weight:0]
